text: The Newberg Graphic is the weekly newspaper of Newberg, Oregon, United States. In January 2013, the paper was sold to the Pamplin Media Group along with five other papers owned by Eagle Newspapers. ==See also== * List of newspapers in Oregon ==References== Category:Newberg, Oregon Category:1907 establishments in Oregon Category:Newspapers published by Pamplin Media Group Category:Oregon Newspaper Publishers Association Category:Publications established in 1907
